lead_paragraph: A Guatemalan sports confederation has voted to reinstate a FIFA-appointed oversight committee, officials said, in a bid to head off the suspension of the country's national soccer federation.

headline.print_headline: Guatemala Sports Body Backs Down in Fight With FIFA
